三角行动助手-Action Assistant Privacy Policy

Delta Action Assistant respects your privacy. This app is designed as an offline tactical assistant for managing maps, markers, operator notes, weapon loadouts, and match records.

We do not require account registration, and we do not collect, upload, sell, or share your personal gameplay data. The content you create in the app is stored locally on your device.

The app may request access to your photo library only when you choose to select a map image. Selected images are used as local map backgrounds and are not uploaded by the app.

The app may display advertisements through third-party advertising SDKs. These services may collect device identifiers, advertising identifiers, approximate device information, or ad interaction data in accordance with their own privacy policies. If required by your system, the app may ask for tracking permission before using advertising identifiers.

The app may use Apple’s in-app review feature to request a rating. This request is handled by Apple and does not provide us with your personal information.

You may export, import, or clear local app data from the Settings page. Clearing data removes locally stored records and map images from your device.

By using this app, you agree to this Privacy Policy. If you do not agree, please stop using the app.

For questions about privacy, please contact the app developer.
